data.description: SELLER OFFERING $14.5K CONCESSION TOWARD BUYER'S INTEREST RATE BUYDOWN OR CLOSING COSTS!! Welcome to your dream home in this highly desirable East Mesa community! A splendidly updated and environmentally friendly property has all the right finishes and amenities. The fresh and inviting feel begins with new flooring, interior/exterior paint, wood-like window coverings, and two fireplaces, all of which contribute to the warmth noticeable throughout. In the kitchen, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, as well as a double oven and breakfast bar, will certainly be a chef's paradise, while the living, dining, bed, and great rooms all boast plenty of space for families of all sizes. Outside, get ready to host incredible gatherings in your private oasis. The pool and built-in BBQ grill are the perfect additions for year-round fun and relaxation. And, with Falcon Hill Park right across the street, you'll have immediate access to playground equipment, fields, and sport courts -- a paradise for kids and adults alike! Don't miss the chance to own your "Forever Home"  See it today!
